RESOURCE.DESCRIPTION: Helio HEC time based query V1.16.25
RESOURCE.INFO: SELECT wind_sw_crossing_time.HEC_id,wind_sw_crossing_time.time_start,wind_sw_crossing_time.time_end FROM wind_sw_crossing_time WHERE time_start>='2003-02-01T00:00:00' AND time_start<='2003-02-10T00:00:00' LIMIT 100 OFFSET 0

FIELD.name: time_start
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Start time for spacecraft in the solar wind.

FIELD.name: time_end
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: End time for spacecraft in the solar wind.
